import React from 'react'
import {ChakraProvider, Container, Box, Stack} from '@chakra-ui/react';

const Section3 = () => {
    return (
        <ChakraProvider>
            <Container maxW="1364px" h="1000px" bg="green.500">
                <Stack direction="column" justify='center'>
                    <Box>
                        <Stack direction="column" spacing="30px">
                            <Box w="264" h="53px"  bg="tomato">
                                sasa
                            </Box>
                            <Box w="674" h="169px"  bg="tomato">
                                asas
                            </Box>
                            <Box w="260" h="48px"  bg="romato">
                                asa
                            </Box>
                        </Stack>
                    </Box>
                    <Box>
                        <Box w="1364" h="231px"  bg="white">
                            1
                        </Box>
                    </Box>
                </Stack>
            </Container>
        </ChakraProvider>
    )
}

export default Section3
